Package: uci.spam.classification
Title: Create a Toy Spam Classifier Using NLP and LDA
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Andrew", "Luyt", , "andrew.luyt@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Using a supplied UCI spam dataset, creates a spam- or ham-classifying
  NLP model. Based on the tutorial at https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL8eNk_zTBST8olxIRFoo0YeXxEOkYdoxi
  by Data Science Dojo.
